This directory vendors the Nim webview binding from https://github.com/neroist/webview
(the file webview.nim), with local fixes noted in docs/DECISIONS.md. It is under
the MIT License, reproduced below.

The C/C++ webview library it wraps is under its own MIT License, kept separately
at libs/webview/LICENSE.

The Microsoft WebView2 SDK headers (used only by the Windows build) are NOT
included here; they are Microsoft's, under Microsoft's own license terms, and are
fetched from Microsoft's NuGet package at build time by scripts/fetch-webview2.ps1.

